Port 22
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication yes
PubkeyAuthentication no
UsePAM no
X11Forwarding no
AllowTcpForwarding no
GatewayPorts no
PermitTunnel no

# Limit resource usage per connection
MaxSessions 2
MaxStartups 10:30:60
LoginGraceTime 20

# Keep connections alive, drop idle ones after 10 min
ClientAliveInterval 60
ClientAliveCountMax 10

# Restrict what users can do
PermitUserEnvironment no
PrintMotd yes
Banner /etc/ssh/banner

# Only allow thief users
AllowUsers thief0 thief1 thief2 thief3 thief4 thief5
